longBusinessSummary: FinCanna Capital Corp. operates as a royalty company for the licensed cannabis industry in the United States. It provides financing for companies operating in the cannabis sector. The company has royalty agreements with Green Compliance Inc.; QVI, Inc.; and Cultivation Technologies, Inc. FinCanna Capital Corp. was incorporated in 2016 is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
